reviewText: This is probably one of the hottest GGW things I seen. The two in the luxury apartment were over the top and worth the price of admission. This was gotten just have something going while we were playing poker and to give someone a diversion from the game for a bit. I will usually get two or three and at the end of the night, someone will buy then from from me, Or I will give them to someone who wants them as I am not all that impressed with this stuff. This one will probably stay in my Library.
